data.description: Inside this comfortable 2-bedroom, 1-bath home, you will find a balanced mix of old-school charm and updated features.  Step into the semi-finished basement for entertaining by the built in bar. The 1-car garage isn't just for parking – there's extra space for storage!   This home is conveniently located on a corner lot just two blocks off Rt 422, making your daily commute a breeze. You will find a grocery store, banks, a playground, and a school close by for your everyday needs. Keep it simple and easy with this down-to-earth home that ticks the boxes for both style and practical living.
